Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.32,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.48,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:28.92,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,空彦 帮那小子实现他的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:33.67,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,师父 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.66,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欧尔麦特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:40.74,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:44.35,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:51.84,MHA_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你们带给我这场绝妙喜剧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.41,MHA_pic,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs90\bord0\blur5\fad(500,0)\t(0,700,\blur0)\t(\fs95)\pos(245,136)}八木俊典
